title: The Townhouse
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffeehouse cafe on Bunbury's main street serving on-trend food, including vegetarian and vegan options for breakfast, brunch, lunch and in-between treats. Vegans could get tofu scramble, a vegan "monkey" burger, raw cheesecake, acai bowl. Close quarter seating inside.
